azon 果種real-time recommendation , 你用excel 未必好易做列"},{"pid":"f54bdf16fad80602e7033e2f08a6d211ded9d37e","tid":909722,"uid":696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"Clustering excel應該做唔到？"},{"pid":"891cb48a36d5f7a4f2598caa682777c9795877de","tid":909722,"uid":135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:23:31.000Z","msg":"每日二百幾GB Excel做唔做到？"},{"pid":"77afa262ab9be0ae242fa9899af24800b675c00e","tid":909722,"uid":12599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:25:38.000Z","msg":"Matlab R Octave 都得<br />\n<br />\n問題係python 自身係一隻半scripting language, 同c/c++/其他language binding 非常之好，syntax 簡單，indentation 統一易上手容易睇，低性能用原生pylib, 高性能可以係c++ 配python.h/swig 去做寫library<br />\n<br />\nlibaray 海量，有原生有c++ 底<br />\n<br />\n除左numpy, matplotlib, scikitlearn, python嘅ML realted package 有:<br />\nopencv <br />\nsimpleitk<br />\nvtk <br />\ntensorflow<br />\ncaffe <br />\nkeras <br />\npytorch <br />\n<br />\n仲有嘅優點係:跨平台，Dev 工具易安裝，environment 穩定,有oop 特性"},{"pid":"0c058a563822b85cf6b88a4b85cd7dbbb8b34996","tid":909722,"uid":33333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:38:32.000Z","msg":"Excel 簡單嘢就做到<br />\n好多data就搞唔掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af36fc3c3e9c216c6db2d122fe1ebf5bbcc0292f","tid":909722,"uid":159659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"無，平時用excel寫neural network"},{"pid":"0956b8b414bef49e123a2f0b1fc44cc55f13ab34","tid":909722,"uid":134974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af36fc3c3e9c216c6db2d122fe1ebf5bbcc0292f","tid":909722,"uid":159659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"無，平時用excel寫neural network"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"Excel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我用紙自己慢慢畫個network出黎"},{"pid":"6a9677562e91f6e34139ed205c7099e084